    <item>
      <title>德国千亿美元交易激增，欧洲其他国家落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-s-100-billion-deal-surge-leaves-rest-of-europe-behind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去几周，德国出现了一系列巨额收购交易，交易额已接近 1000 亿美元，增幅超过欧洲其他地区，让银行家们对今年剩余时间的复苏充满希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-s-100-billion-deal-surge-leaves-rest-of-europe-behind</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国仍对电动汽车关税持怀疑态度：舒尔茨顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/germany-remains-skeptical-on-ev-tariffs-scholz-adviser</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨的首席经济顾问约尔格·库基斯表示，德国对欧盟对中国制造的进口电动汽车征收关税仍持怀疑态度，并仍希望在周五成员国就该提案进行表决之前通过谈判达成解决方案。库基斯在柏林全球对话 2024 会议间隙与弗朗辛·拉夸进行了交谈，还讨论了德国经济以及为提高增长率所做的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/germany-remains-skeptical-on-ev-tariffs-scholz-adviser</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>装满炸药的无人驾驶船在红海撞上油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/explosive-packed-drone-boat-slams-into-oil-tanker-in-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘满载炸药的无人驾驶船在驶过也门海岸时撞上了一艘油轮，这表明以色列的空袭并未阻止该国胡塞武装分子袭击商业航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/explosive-packed-drone-boat-slams-into-oil-tanker-in-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:38:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员增加对欧洲央行本月降息的押注，全球债券市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的迹象表明欧洲经济需要放松货币政策，欧洲政府债券价格上涨，交易员为欧洲更快降息做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/europe-leads-bond-rally-with-october-cut-almost-fully-priced</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
